wikipedia_page.main: Hugo Carl Emil Muecke (8 July 1842 – 6 June 1929) was a businessman and politician in the colony and State of South Australia.

response: *Isabel May Sunter (c. 1875 – 20 February 1947) married Louis Hugo Muecke (7 February 1873 – c. 25 July 1943) on 4 April 1899. Louis was a son of Hugo Carl Emil Muecke, consul for Germany.
